class.rdfs:comment: A single item within a larger data feed.
class.rdfs:label: DataFeedItem

schema:dateCreated.rdfs:comment: The date on which the CreativeWork was created or the item was added to a DataFeed.
schema:dateCreated.rdfs:label: dateCreated

schema:dateDeleted.rdfs:comment: The datetime the item was removed from the DataFeed.
schema:dateDeleted.rdfs:label: dateDeleted

schema:dateModified.rdfs:comment: The date on which the CreativeWork was most recently modified or when the item's entry was modified within a DataFeed.
schema:dateModified.rdfs:label: dateModified

schema:item.rdfs:comment: An entity represented by an entry in a list or data feed (e.g. an 'artist' in a list of 'artists').
schema:item.rdfs:label: item
